        <num>25-4-2</num>
        <content>
          <p>As used in this chapter, the term:</p>
          <p>(Ga. L. 1971, p. 693, § 2; Ga. L. 1987, p. 373, § 1; Ga. L. 2003, p. 888, § 4; Ga. L. 2005, p. 619, § 1/SB 308; Ga. L. 2008, p. 243, § 2/SB 414; Ga. L. 2016, p. 64, § 2/HB 727; Ga. L. 2020, p. 515, § 4/SB 342.)</p>
          <p>The 2016 amendment,
      effective April 26, 2016, inserted "a recruit or" near the beginning of paragraph (6); and added paragraph (8.1).</p>
          <p>The 2020 amendment,
      effective January 1, 2021, substituted "'on an hourly or salaried basis," for "by" in paragraph (9) and added paragraph (10).</p>
        </content>
